      "created": 1778967703,
      "updated": 1778967703
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10ea650000000000bc5149",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779493477,
      "updated": 1779493478
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10ea660000000000bc514a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779493479,
      "updated": 1779493479
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08e47f00000000008e872a",
      "text": " [文学]媒体としての [Cosense] に最近ちょっと可能性を感じている[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778967703,
      "updated": 1778967771
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08e48500000000008e872c",
      "text": "  [デライト]文学の知見を輸入したい",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778967709,
      "updated": 1778969525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08eb9d00000000008e8732",
      "text": "   ぶっちゃけ、私の文章ちょっとイイでしょ",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778969525,
      "updated": 1779021411
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08e4fa00000000008e872d",
      "text": "  Cosense 的[箇条書き]とデライト的[美文章]の[アウフヘーベン]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778967826,
      "updated": 1779020478
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b2a60000000000540cb7",
      "text": "   スローガンは「[* 美文章分かつべし]」",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779020479,
      "updated": 1779020590
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b3150000000000540cb8",
      "text": "   ツッコめる文学",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779020590,
      "updated": 1779020593
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08e70d00000000008e872f",
      "text": "    Cosense 的ツッコミを包摂してしまう文学",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778968357,
      "updated": 1778968384
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b1210000000000018ed1",
      "text": "   美しい文章とは明晰な文章という考え方（[明晰主義]）があるので、実は文学論の観点からも一定の妥当性がある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779020089,
      "updated": 1779020230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b1ba0000000000018ed2",
      "text": "    「美文晰文」で行こう！",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779020243,
      "updated": 1779020263
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b23c0000000000540cb6",
      "text": "   そういえば[ウィトゲンシュタイン]が似たようなことしていたような",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779020372,
      "updated": 1779020385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08e47f00000000008e872b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778967704,
      "updated": 1778967704
    }
  ]
}